-- Heir Loom's Brault Says Coffee Is a `Black Gold' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-07-31T19:22:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-31/heir-loom-s-brault-says-coffee-is-a-black-gold-audio-.html
Len Brault, chief executive officer 
and founder Heir Loom Coffee, says coffee is a "black gold" and 
is one of the two biggest commodities in the world, the other 
being oil. Brault discusses how he went into the coffee business
and the choices he made in business development.Brault talked to
Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on July 
30, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:41
 